authors: Michael Edwards, Tom Dudfield, Chris van de Steeg, Reinoud van Dalen
description:
This is a forked version based on Mike Edwards' with changes from http://github.com/csteeg/glass.mapper & http://github.com/rvandalen/glass.mapper .
    Only install this package if you intend to use your own DI setup, otherwise install Glass.Mapper.Sc.CastleWindsor.
    
		An ORM for Sitecore. Map item data from Sitecore straight onto objects. Allows you to map fields,
		relationships and queries as well as supporting the Page Editor.
releaseNotes: This is a pre-release version of the package.
